RedmiBook pro 15 
Preparation 
   1) cp DebianXXX.iso to usb 
         check which /dev device for usb
         unmount all mount point which on usb device
         cp DebianXXX.iso to usb
   2) Reactivate the unused space for usb
         fdisk /dev/XXX for creating a new partition 
         mkfs.XXX with new partition on USB device
         
         
Installation
1) Only avaliable for Debian11, for 3K display set scale to 200% in Display setting
   Remember to set /etc/apt/source.list to china source for fast download.

2) Wireless Network  (RTK 8852AE) use driver https://github.com/lwfinger/rtw89 suppose > kernel 5.4 but tested ok with 5.1 in Debian11

3) Display driver can be installed with Debian internal amd driver package "apt search --names-only firm|grep amd" 
   ,Note only able to change display refresh frame not resoultion so far
   ,In case of wrong resoultion set then use command line go to ~/.config/ reset the display setting.Setting is avalid by account only. also can create a new user to login 

4) Use ibus to install chinese 

5) Install battery function TLP - Optimize Linux Laptop Battery Life call "TLP start" ,Seems set in initr

6ï¼‰Install Python with venv
      python -m venv $PathWithNewEnv
      source $PathWithNewEnv/bin/activate
      
   
